         <abstract id="aspace_5e01ecfa52f480fc32c67514433a03e4">The Dwight / Edgewood Project is a non-profit organization that brings children together with Yale School of Drama and Yale Repertory Theatre artists to create theater. This collection documents the activities of the project from 1995-2008 through photographs, scripts, programs, and administrative papers.</abstract>
