      <acqinfo id="aspace_98b9af0ef12c66bc472fa11db63e0896">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Dwight / Edgewood Project Collection was housed in the former Drama Library until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
