      <scopecontent id="aspace_fed29bf24572f2c0cfc87e6b333b33d5">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Dwight/Edgewood Project (D/EP) is a non-profit organization that brings children together with Yale School of Drama and Yale Repertory Theatre artists to create theater. This collection documents the activities of the project from 1995-2008 through photographs, scripts, programs, and administrative papers.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
